                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.00/8175: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-02-01T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 1, 1927—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>41. Your telegram [105], February 1, 10 p.m. Procedure outlined in paragraphs 1
                    and 2 is approved. I shall withhold publication here until you advise me that
                    message has been delivered. For publication Department will use text as amended
                    in its telegram 35, January 31, 1 p.m.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
